Summary Until Now

I am standing really low of my goal. Getting less than 40% marks in Allen and FIITJEE Test. Currently i am getting ranks near 150 in allen jee advanced tests. I want to escalate them to <= 10 rank before JEE Advanced. There are about 40 days for JEE Advanced and my goal is to get rank <=10 in JEE Advanced.

Today, a large part of my time (2.5 hr) is spent in creating this thing. Still hoping that it's worth it. 

Today's Progress is that i was able to complete all GRPs for 1 day. However i was not able to Dq them or tests that i have given in last 2 days. Tomorrow's goal will be to get Rating Score of 55. 

An upcoming danger is Vaishnavy is coming back. She can be a big trouble as she is a fool and thinks of nothing. So, I will try to get away from any arguments and will try to waste no time.
